Sorce's Privacy Policy
Last Updated: Tue Jul. 29, 2024
Introduction
Welcome to Sorce's Privacy Policy. We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This policy outlines our practices concerning data collection, usage, and security.
Information We Collect
Non-Collection Policy:
We do not collect any personal information from our users, except when they opt to subscribe to our services.
Location Data:
We collect location data from your device when you use our app to provide location-based services and improve your experience. This includes your device's GPS coordinates and general location information.
Subscription Information:
During subscription, we only collect necessary payment information, such as credit/debit card details, to process payments.
Use of Collected Information
Payment Processing:
The sole purpose of collecting financial information is to process subscription payments. We do not use this information for any other purposes.
Security Measures:
We employ various security measures to ensure the protection of your payment information.
Sharing of Information
Non-Disclosure:
We do not share, sell, rent, or trade any personal information with third parties for their commercial purposes.
Legal Requirements:
We may disclose your information if required by law or if we believe in good faith that such action is necessary to comply with legal processes.
Data Retention
Retention Period:
We retain your payment information only as long as necessary to complete the transaction and comply with our legal obligations.
Deletion of Data:
Upon request, we will delete your personal information from our records, except for any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.
Google User Data
Third-Party AI Tools:
Any Google user data from Google's Workspace APIs
ARE NOT
used to develop, improve, or train generalized/non-personalized AI and/or ML models.
Contact Us
Questions and Concerns:
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
founders@sorce.jobs
Feedback:
We welcome your feedback and suggestions to improve our privacy practices.
Policy Updates
Amendments:
We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
Delete Account and Data
Account Deletion:
To delete your account on the Sorce app, follow these steps:
Open the Sorce App:
Launch the app on your device.
Navigate to Profile:
Tap on your profile icon to access your account settings.
Go to Settings:
Within your profile, find and select the 'Settings' option.
Delete Account:
Scroll down to find the 'Delete Account' option and select it. Follow any additional prompts to confirm the deletion.
Data Deletion:
When you delete your account, all your personal data will be permanently deleted from our records, except for any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.
Assistance:
If you encounter any issues or prefer assistance, you can contact the Sorce team directly at
founders@sorce.jobs
for help with deleting your account and data.
Conclusion
Your privacy is of utmost importance to us at Sorce. We are committed to ensuring the security and confidentiality of your personal information.